dc_title_s: Stokes State Forest, New Jersey 1948, brochure front
dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Maps of Stokes State Forest in Sussex County, N.J. part of multi-page brochure. First side is outside cover of brochure with three photographs and descriptions of the lakes and waterways, camp grounds, picnic areas and hiking trails. Second sheet is map showing the Lake Ocquittunk section with inset of the central section of the park. Legends indicate paved roads, unpaved trails, streams and other waterways, camp grounds and park office.
